## 2. State Machine Map

```
pending ŌöĆŌöĆ(accept)ŌöĆŌöĆŌ¢║ accepted ŌöĆŌöĆ(start)ŌöĆŌöĆŌ¢║ in_progress ŌöĆŌöĆ(complete)ŌöĆŌöĆŌ¢║ completed ŌöĆŌöĆ(payment)ŌöĆŌöĆŌ¢║ paid
   Ōöé                     Ōöé
   ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ(cancel)ŌöĆŌöĆŌ¢║ cancelled ŌŚäŌöĆŌöĆ(cancel)ŌöĆŌöĆŌöś
   Ōöé
   ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ(auto-timeout at T+60s)ŌöĆŌöĆŌ¢║ cancelled
```

### Transition Guards (must be preserved exactly)

| Transition | From | To | Guard |
|---|---|---|---|
| accept | `pending` | `accepted` | Worker must not be blocked (`isBlocked === false`) |
| start | `accepted` | `in_progress` | None |
| complete | `in_progress` | `completed` | None |
| cancel (no fee) | `pending` | `cancelled` | Clears active timer |
| cancel (with fee) | `accepted` | `cancelled` | Records `metadata.cancellationFee = { amount: 50, currency: 'INR' }` |
| auto-timeout | `pending` | `cancelled` | Triggered by 60s in-memory timer |
| payment verify | `completed` | `paid` + `paymentStatus: 'paid'` | `status === 'completed'` strict check |

### Side Effects Per Transition (must be preserved exactly)

| Transition | Socket Event | Telegram | Timer |
|---|---|---|---|
| create | `booking:new` ŌåÆ worker socket | `sendBookingAlertToWorker` | Start 60s countdown |
| accept | `booking:accepted` ŌåÆ customer socket | ŌĆö | Cancel countdown |
| start | `booking:started` ŌåÆ `booking_{id}` room | ŌĆö | ŌĆö |
| complete | `booking:completed` ŌåÆ `booking_{id}` room | ŌĆö | ŌĆö |
| cancel | `booking:cancelled` ŌåÆ `booking_{id}` room | ŌĆö | Cancel countdown if pending |
| auto-timeout | `booking:timeout` ŌåÆ `booking_{id}` room | ŌĆö | Self-clears |

