## 8. Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Affected Component | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| State machine transition logic divergence | ­¤ö┤ CRITICAL | All 7 use cases | Port guards verbatim; 14 existing tests remain green throughout |
| Timer state divergence (2 maps today) | ­¤¤Ī MEDIUM | `reminderService.js` | Deferred to Phase 3.5 ŌĆö clean module calls `reminderService` directly |
| `Booking` model name resolution via proxy | ­¤¤Ī MEDIUM | 4 populate chains | Idempotent guard + explicit populate verification script |
| Payment status gate breaking | ­¤¤Ī MEDIUM | `paymentController.verifyPaymentSignature` | Proxy covers transparently; `paymentRedirect.test.js` confirms |
| Telegram hardcoded chat ID | ­¤¤ó LOW | `CreateBookingUseCase` | Copied as-is ŌĆö existing tech debt, not introduced here |
| Double Mongoose model registration | ­¤¤ó LOW | `BookingSchema.js` | `mongoose.models.Booking \|\| mongoose.model(...)` guard |
| Chat route on booking router | ­¤¤ó LOW | `GET /bookings/chats/:id` | Included in clean `bookingRoutes.js` |

