## 10. Rollback Strategy

| Step | Rollback Action |
|---|---|
| After Phase A (new files only) | Delete `src/modules/booking/` ŌĆö zero legacy impact |
| After Phase C (proxy deployed) | `git checkout -- src/models/Booking.js` ŌĆö legacy schema restored instantly |
| After any test failure | `git stash` ŌĆö legacy routes remain active, no user disruption |
| Emergency | `git revert <Phase3.3 commit>` ŌĆö single atomic revert |

